data.name: lucid-mono
data.description: Enterprise-grade high-accuracy transcription for single language content (English optimized). Supports batch and real-time streaming.

data.name: lucid-multi
data.description: Enterprise-grade multilingual transcription with code-switching support. Supports batch and real-time streaming.

data.name: lucid-agent
data.description: Enterprise-grade transcription optimized for conversational content. Supports batch and real-time streaming.

data.name: lucid-lite
data.description: Enterprise-grade cost-effective transcription model for high-volume use. Supports batch and real-time streaming.

data.name: aura-lite
data.description: Fast TTS model optimized for real-time applications. Supports 74 languages, expression tags, ~200ms first byte latency. Cost: 1 credit per character.

data.name: aura-prime
data.description: Balanced TTS model with excellent quality and enhanced prosody. Supports 74 languages, expression tags, ~400ms first byte latency. Cost: 1 credit per character.

data.name: aura-max
data.description: Premium TTS model for audiobooks and professional media. Highest quality, natural prosody, expression tags, ~800ms first byte latency. Supports 74 languages. Cost: 1 credit per character.

data.name: rapid-flash
data.description: Ultra-fast low-latency TTS (~100ms first byte). Optimized for IVR and notifications. Supports 18 languages. No expression tags. Cost: 1 credit per character.

data.name: rapid-max
data.description: Fast TTS model with better quality than Rapid Flash (~150ms first byte). Supports 50+ languages. No expression tags. Cost: 2 credits per character.
